Class ExtractDocField

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ephesoft.dcma.regex.util.ExtractDocField

  • public class ExtractDocField
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to extract the document fields. This will parse the file, update the file. After inserting all the document level fields this class will actually persists the whole data to the batch.xml file.
